('pond-heron', 'Indian Pond Heron', 'Ardeola grayii', 'A small heron with cryptic plumage that transforms in flight. Common near water across Nepal.', 'BIRD', 'LEAST_CONCERN', 'COMMON', 'Ponds, marshes, and agricultural fields', '100-1500m', '25000', false, false, 'Indian Pond Herons appear brown when standing but flash white wings in flight.'),
('cattle-egret', 'Cattle Egret', 'Bubulcus ibis', 'A small, stocky heron that follows livestock to catch disturbed insects. Very common across Nepal.', 'BIRD', 'LEAST_CONCERN', 'COMMON', 'Agricultural fields, pastures, and wetlands', '100-2000m', '30000', false, false, 'Cattle Egrets have spread across most of the world from their original African range.');
